reviews.review_text: - I like this better than the 48K. It sounds much clearer to my ears, don't know why. It's also a terrific show!

The only Dead show I ever saw This show was the only time I ever got to see the Grateful Dead. The energy of the show was unlike anything I've ever experienced. Glad to finally have a copy to relive the magic. Kind of bittersweet as well since the friend I went with is no longer with us.
